<p>Other examples:</p>
<ul>
<li>Analysis of the <a href="/wiki/Rational_Unified_Process" title="Rational Unified Process" class="mw-redirect">Rational Unified Process</a> as a Process, <sup id="cite_ref-29" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-29" title=""><span>[</span>30<span>]</span></a></sup></li>
