</ul>
<p><a name="Base_for_other_Enterprise_Architecture_framework" id="Base_for_other_Enterprise_Architecture_framework"></a></p>
<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Zachman_framework&amp;action=edit&amp;section=16" title="Edit section: Base for other Enterprise Architecture framework">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Base for other Enterprise Architecture framework</span></h3>
<p>Less obvious are the ways the original Zachman framework has stimulated the development of other <a href="/wiki/Enterprise_Architecture_framework" title="Enterprise Architecture framework">Enterprise Architecture frameworks</a>, such as in the <a href="/wiki/NIST_Enterprise_Architecture_Model" title="NIST Enterprise Architecture Model">NIST Enterprise Architecture Model</a>, the <a href="/wiki/C4ISR" title="C4ISR">C4ISR</a> AE, the DOE AE, and the <a href="/wiki/DoDAF" title="DoDAF" class="mw-redirect">DoDAF</a>:</p>
<center>
<table class="gallery" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
<tr>
<td>
<div class="gallerybox" style="width: 155px;">
<div class="thumb" style="padding: 13px 0; width: 150px;">
<div style="margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; width: 120px;"><a href="/wiki/File:NIST_Enterprise_Architecture_Model.jpg" class="image" title="NIST Enterprise Architecture Model.jpg"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/d/d0/NIST_Enterprise_Architecture_Model.jpg/105px-NIST_Enterprise_Architecture_Model.jpg" width="105" height="120" border="0" /></a></div>
</div>
<div class="gallerytext">
<p>NIST Enterprise Architecture Model.<sup id="cite_ref-CIOC99_24-6" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-CIOC99-24" title=""><span>[</span>25<span>]</span></a></sup></p>
</div>
</div>
</td>
<td>
<div class="gallerybox" style="width: 155px;">
<div class="thumb" style="padding: 37px 0; width: 150px;">
<div style="margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; width: 120px;"><a href="/wiki/File:LISI_Reference_Model_1997.jpg" class="image" title="LISI Reference Model 1997.jpg"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/e5/LISI_Reference_Model_1997.jpg/120px-LISI_Reference_Model_1997.jpg" width="120" height="71" border="0" /></a></div>
</div>
<div class="gallerytext">
<p><a href="/wiki/C4ISR" title="C4ISR">C4ISR</a> AE, 1997.</p>
